    "159645723": {
      "title": "About ICOLC and the ICOLC Statement on the Global Economic Crisis and Its Impact on Consortial Licenses",
      "abstract": "The International Coalition of Library Consortia (ICOLC) and its role in library consortial approaches to content acquisition is briefly explained. A copy of its most recent statement on the global economic crisis and the resulting implications for libraries’ budgets is also provided."
